		<div id="container">
<div id="content">        <div class="spacer"></div>             <span id="shash-30871"><div class="post" id="post-30871">                    <h1><a href="http://trilema.com/2011/the-night-that-music-died/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to The night that music died">The night that music died</a></h1>                        <div class="date">                                     Saturday, 24 December, Year 3 d.Tr.&nbsp;|&nbsp;Author: <a href="http://trilema.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Mircea Popescu">Mircea Popescu</a>                                                        </div>

                        <div class="entry">
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: left;">If love truly is going out of fashion forever, which I do not believe, then along with our nurtured indifference to each other will be an even more contemptuous indifference to each others' objects of reverence. I thought it was Iggy Stooge, you thought it was Joni Mitchell or whoever else seemed to speak for your own private, entirely circumscribed situation's many pains and few ecstasies. We will continue to fragment in this manner, because solipsism holds all the cards at present; it is a king whose domain engulfs even Elvis's. But I can guarantee you one thing: we will never again agree on anything as we agreed on Elvis. So I won't bother saying good-bye to his corpse. I will say good-bye to you.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Sa va traduc ? Hai ca va traduc, ca-mi sunteti simpatici.</p>
<blockquote><p>Daca iubirea chiar se demodeaza pentru totdeauna, ceea ce eu nu cred, atunci alaturi de o cultivata indiferenta fata de ceilalti vom nutri o si mai dispretuitoare indiferenta pentru idolii celorlalti. Eu am crezut ca-i Iggy Stooge, tu ai crezut ca-i Joni Mitchell sau oricine altcineva parea sa vorbeasca numeroaselor dureri si putinelor extazuri complet circumscrise propriei tale situatii. Vom continua sa ne fragmentam de-aceasta maniera, pentru ca solipsismul are toate atuurile in prezent ; e un rege a carui regat inghite pina si regatul lui Elvis. Dar pot sa va garantez un lucru : nu vom mai fi niciodata de acord pe nici o tema cum am fost de acord asupra lui Elvis. Asa ca nu ma voi obosi sa-mi iau ramas bun de la cadavrul lui. Imi voi lua ramas-bun de la voi.</p></blockquote>
<p><a href="http://trilema.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/cine-i-mustaciosul.jpg"><img class="alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-30872" title="cine-i-mustaciosul" src="http://trilema.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/cine-i-mustaciosul-150x150.jpg" alt="cine-i-mustaciosul" width="150" height="150" /></a>Asta se intimpla, cum poate ghiciti, in 1977. Acum treizeci si patru de ani. Femei care s-au nascut dupa aceea au copii deja, si daca n-au copii deja lumea le intreaba uimita cum se face ca n-au copii inca, si ce mai asteapta. Adevaru-i ca a trecut destul de mult timp.</p>
<p>Cuvintele se dovedesc, iata, profetice. Sunt curios daca stiti sa-mi spuneti cine le-a emis. V-as oferi o poza, sa va usurez sarcina, da' mi-e c-o gasiti cu google si imi stricati tot experimentul. Asa ca am procesat-o putin. Cine-i mustaciosul ?</p>
<p>Si daca stiti cine-i mustaciosul, intrebare suplimentara <span style="background-color:#d3d3d3" id="select">: care-s costurile faptului ca noi sedeam intr-o pivnita si numaram cincinale in timp ce <a href="http://trilema.com/2011/howl-de-alan-ginsberg/">evreii netalentati</a> cu pretentii la boema isi spargeau gaozu' pe zece dolari mototoliti ? Ce-am pierdut, cit ne-a</span> costat ? Ce-avem de recuperat ? Unde suntem, ce-am ramas, ce stim si cit intelegem ? Cit de in urma suntem ?</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>A long, long time ago<br />
I can still remember how that music used to make me smile<br />
And I knew if I had my chance that I could make those people dance<br />
And maybe they'd be happy for a while</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">So bye, bye Miss American Pie<br />
Drove my Chevy to the levee but the levee was dry<br />
And them good old boys were drinking whiskey and rye<br />
Singing this'll be the day that I die, this'll be the day that I die</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">Did you write the book of love and do you have faith in God above<br />
If the Bible tells you so? Now do you believe in rock and roll?<br />
Can music save your mortal soul?<br />
And can you teach me how to dance real slow?</p>
<p></em></p>

